display.title: Cetane-boosted Diesel
description: &&aCetane-Boosted Diesel&&r is &&650% more energy dense&&r than regular &&aDiesel&&r, and only requires 1 part &&dTetranitromethane (TNM)&&r for every 50 parts &&aDiesel&&r. What a steal, right?

The catch comes in the complexity of making &&dTNM&&r. In order to concoct it, you must react &&aNitric Acid&&r with either &&dEthenone&&r or &&aMethyl Acetate&&r, both of which have quite an involved process themselves!
